Project Name: IMS Database Monitor using Power BI and Microsoft Power Automate
Tools used: JCL, Rexx, Power Automate, Microsoft One Drive, Power BI

Problem: One of the best practices in IMS Database support is to weekly monitor the databases using provided tools by vendors like IBM, BMC. But, those tools create the reports readable for mainframe users, but they are not so friendly for managers or other people who make decisions.

The tool in case is Space Monitor by IBM, which runs under Mainframe and uses specific functions to create the report. IBM gave us an example here:
